    "Then, the dimensionality of these features can be minimized by applying the optimization technique.",
    "(8) X n j = y(n), y n + j, y n + 2j, y n + 3j,.",
    "11) FD T = log 10 ω d avg log 10 d 1n d avg = log 10 h log 10 d 1n ω + log 10 h (12)",
    "To increase classification accuracy and efficiency, the best features are chosen using the GBSO technique once the set of features has been extracted.",
    "The hybrid BF and GA method known as genetically bacterial swarm optimisation (GBSO) in the current work uses three genetic operators-crossover, mutation, and selection-as well as BF's chemotactic mechanism to perform local search."
